const App = () => {
    return ( 
        <Router>
            
                <Link to="/">
                    Layout
                </Link> 
                <Link to="/viewabout">
                    ViewAbout
                </Link>    
            


            <Switch>
                <Route  path="/" exact>
                    <Layout />
                </Route>
                <Route  path="/viewabout">
                    <ViewAbout />
                </Route>
                <Route  path="/service">
                    <Service />
                </Route>
            </Switch>
        </Router>
        
    )
}

export default App;
